data.description: This Cornerstone home might truly be THE ONE. As a one-year-old built home, 2605 Moonlight Circle embodies everything you desire in a new home without the usual wait time, yet with all the upgrades you crave. A board & batten vinyl siding, front porch ready for every seasonal decor, and elegant stone columns immediately greet you. Moonlighting as your dream home come to life, you'll enjoy the open floor concept connecting the kitchen, dining, and living room complemented by a fireplace for cozy evenings. The heart of the home - the kitchen - includes a massive walk-in pantry, quartz countertops, and upgraded beverage center. Bringing in ample natural light, the sliding glass door also leads to a newly landscaped outdoor haven with a charming stone walkway and heated in-ground pool perfect for entertaining or relaxing. Upstairs offers 4 bedrooms, a loft, laundry room, and primary en suite. There's plenty of additional room options on every level including the basement that is ready to finish or keep as additional storage space. This Rolling Meadows gem is a must see and we're excited to show you during open house Sat 12/2 from 11am-1pm!
